# Game Logic

- Pure TypeScript — no React imports in game logic
- Colocated `*.test.ts` next to logic; register new test files in `package.json` `"test"` script
- Combat state schema: `src/lib/schemas/combat-state.ts`
- Player combat actions → Postgres RPC; DM → direct `combat_state` persist
- Follow existing section-header style (`// ── ... ──`) in larger lib files
